{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">了解离子反应发生的条件。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">BaCl<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&nbsp;+&nbsp;Cu<span style=\"color:#000000\">SO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">4</span></sub>&nbsp;= Ba<span style=\"color:#000000\">SO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">4</span></sub>&darr; +CuCl<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Cu<span style=\"color:#000000\">SO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">4</span></sub>&nbsp;&nbsp;+2NaOH&nbsp;= Cu<span style=\"color:#000000\">(</span>OH<span style=\"color:#000000\">)</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&darr;&nbsp;+Na<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">SO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">4</span></sub></span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：试管、胶头滴管。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：硫酸铜溶液、氯化钡溶液、氢氧化钠溶液。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">分别在两支试管中加入一定量的硫酸铜溶液，然后分别滴加氯化钡溶液和氢氧化钠溶液，观察实验现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">滴加氯化钡溶液的试管中，产生白色沉淀；滴加氢氧化钠溶液的试管中，产生蓝色沉淀。</span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}